	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">tepples wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Can <em>Action 52</em> be split into its components?</div>
<br />Yes it can.  You can extract each 32k from inside, add the VROM, and call it a mapper 0 game.  Nesticle will even play them.  Only problem is that some games bankswitch half way through (Billy Bob after level 2, Cheetahmen each 2 levels).
<br />Oddly, the VROM bankswitching is almost identical to CNROM.  (set cheetahmen 2 to mapper 3 and you can still watch the intro)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


